title: Sabtain Raza wins PP-274 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League (N) candidate, Muhammad Sabtain Raza has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-274, Muzaffargarh-VII by securing 44,560 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate, Shahzad Rasool Khan who bagged 37,670 votes.
The votersâ€™ turnout remained 53.81%.
